A minimalistic text editor by grunfink - public domain

This is a rewrite from scratch of qw 0.14. It features:

* Infinite undo/redo levels.
* Wordwrapping by default.
* Full utf-8 support (arbitrary encodings not supported).
* Syntax highlighting (configurable, with a few very common languages included).
* Configurable colors.
* Configurable key remapping.
* Multiplatform: ANSI terminal (Linux, BSD, UNIX, etc) and MS Windows.
* Clean codebase, source code comments.
